        <mxCell id="rules" value="&lt;b&gt;Key Business Rules&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;1. Users specialize into exactly one role row by user.role.&lt;br&gt;2. Provider skills require manager approval before booking.&lt;br&gt;3. Provider appointments cannot overlap pending/accepted/in_progress appointments.&lt;br&gt;4. Provider unavailable blocks also prevent overlapping appointments.&lt;br&gt;5. Booking rate snapshot includes schedule surcharge: weekday after-hours +20%, weekend +10%, both +30%.&lt;br&gt;6. Actual payment requires completed appointment and actual_hours.&lt;br&gt;7. Reviews are only receiver-provider or provider-receiver, one per direction." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;fontSize=14;fontFamily=Verdana;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
